o you do irrigation repair?\nA: Yes, sprinkler repair, winterization, and new system install."}]'::jsonb, updated_at = now() WHERE industry_id = 'landscape';
UPDATE public.industry_template_packs SET kb_seed_documents = '[{"name": "Pool & Spa - Services Overview", "content": "Welcome to our pool & spa business. Weekly pool service, equipment repair (pumps, filters, heaters), opening/closing, leak detection, resurfacing, salt cell replacement, and spa service.\n\nServing residential and commercial customers with licensed, insured, and experienced professionals."}, {"name": "Pool & Spa - Pricing & Process", "content": "Our pricing approach for pool & spa: Weekly service from $150/month. Equipment repair $200-$1,200. Opening/closing $250-$450.\n\nProcess: 1) Schedule a consultation or service visit. 2) Receive a detailed quote upfront. 3) Approve and we get to work. 4) Follow up to confirm satisfaction.", "faqs": [{"question": "Do you offer weekly maintenance?", "answer": "Yes, full-service weekly visits including chemistry, vacuum, and equipment check.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Can you fix any pool equipment?", "answer": "Yes, all major brands of pumps, filters, heaters, and salt systems.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Do you do pool openings?", "answer": "Yes, full opening/closing service with safety cover handling.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Do you handle vinyl liner replacement?", "answer": "Yes, we measure, order, and install custom liners.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Can you find a leak?", "answer": "Yes, electronic leak detection without destructive testing.", "category": "general"}]}, {"name": "Pool & Spa - Frequently Asked Questions", "content": "Here are common questions and answers about our services:\n\nQ: Do you offer weekly maintenance?\nA: Yes, full-service weekly visits including chemistry, vacuum, and equipment check.\n\nQ: Can you fix any pool equipment?\nA: Yes, all major brands of pumps, filters, heaters, and salt systems.\n\nQ: Do you do pool openings?\nA: Yes, full opening/closing service with safety cover handling.\n\nQ: Do you handle vinyl liner replacement?\nA: Yes, we measure, order, and install custom liners.\n\nQ: Can you find a leak?\nA: Yes, electronic leak detection without destructive testing."}]'::jsonb, updated_at = now() WHERE industry_id = 'pool_spa';
UPDATE public.industry_template_packs SET kb_seed_documents = '[{"name": "Auto Care - Services Overview", "content": "Welcome to our auto care business. Full-service auto repair: oil changes, brakes, alignment, diagnostics, tires, A/C service, transmission, engine repair, state inspections, and pre-purchase inspections.\n\nServing residential and commercial customers with licensed, insured, and experienced professionals."}, {"name": "Auto Care - Pricing & Process", "content": "Our pricing approach for auto care: Oil change from $49. Brake service $200-$600/axle. Diagnostic $129. Free estimates on major repairs.\n\nProcess: 1) Schedule a consultation or service visit. 2) Receive a detailed quote upfront. 3) Approve and we get to work. 4) Follow up to confirm satisfaction.", "faqs": [{"question": "Do you work on all makes?", "answer": "Yes, domestic and import including European.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Are your techs certified?", "answer": "Yes, ASE-certified technicians.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Do you offer a warranty?", "answer": "Yes, 24-month/24,000-mile nationwide warranty on most repairs.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Can I get a loaner car?", "answer": "Loaners available by appointment for major repairs.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Do you do state inspections?", "answer": "Yes, official state inspection station.", "category": "general"}]}, {"name": "Auto Care - Frequently Asked Questions", "content": "Here are common questions and answers about our services:\n\nQ: Do you work on all makes?\nA: Yes, domestic and import including European.\n\nQ: Are your techs certified?\nA: Yes, ASE-certified technicians.\n\nQ: Do you offer a warranty?\nA: Yes, 24-month/24,000-mile nationwide warranty on most repairs.\n\nQ: Can I get a loaner car?\nA: Loaners available by appointment for major repairs.\n\nQ: Do you do state inspections?\nA: Yes, official state inspection station."}]'::jsonb, updated_at = now() WHERE industry_id = 'auto_care';
