Yes, retail haircare, skincare, and tools available in salon."}]'::jsonb, updated_at = now() WHERE industry_id = 'beauty_wellness';
UPDATE public.industry_template_packs SET kb_seed_documents = '[{"name": "Real Estate - Services Overview", "content": "Welcome to our real estate business. Buyer and seller representation, property valuations (CMA), listing services, showings, open houses, transaction coordination, investor and relocation services.\n\nServing residential and commercial customers with licensed, insured, and experienced professionals."}, {"name": "Real Estate - Pricing & Process", "content": "Our pricing approach for real estate: Standard commission negotiable. Free home valuations. No upfront fees for buyers in most cases.\n\nProcess: 1) Schedule a consultation or service visit. 2) Receive a detailed quote upfront. 3) Approve and we get to work. 4) Follow up to confirm satisfaction.", "faqs": [{"question": "How much is my home worth?", "answer": "Free comparative market analysis (CMA) - schedule online.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "How long until my home sells?", "answer": "Average days on market in our area; depends on price/condition - we''ll review.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Do you work with first-time buyers?", "answer": "Yes, including down payment assistance program guidance.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "What''s your commission?", "answer": "Negotiable based on services and price point.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Can you help me relocate?", "answer": "Yes, we have a national relocation network.", "category": "general"}]}, {"name": "Real Estate - Frequently Asked Questions", "content": "Here are common questions and answers about our services:\n\nQ: How much is my home worth?\nA: Free comparative market analysis (CMA) - schedule online.\n\nQ: How long until my home sells?\nA: Average days on market in our area; depends on price/condition - we''ll review.\n\nQ: Do you work with first-time buyers?\nA: Yes, including down payment assistance program guidance.\n\nQ: What''s your commission?\nA: Negotiable based on services and price point.\n\nQ: Can you help me relocate?\nA: Yes, we have a national relocation network."}]'::jsonb, updated_at = now() WHERE industry_id = 'real_estate';
UPDATE public.industry_template_packs SET kb_seed_documents = '[{"name": "Restaurants - Services Overview", "content": "Welcome to our restaurants business. Dine-in, takeout, delivery, online ordering, catering, private events, and gift cards. Menu features [chef-curated dishes/regional cuisine].\n\nServing residential and commercial customers with licensed, insured, and experienced professionals."}, {"name": "Restaurants - Pricing & Process", "content": "Our pricing approach for restaurants: Entrees $14-$32. Family meals and catering packages available. Happy hour and lunch specials weekdays.\n\nProcess: 1) Schedule a consultation or service visit. 2) Receive a detailed quote upfront. 3) Approve and we get to work. 4) Follow up to confirm satisfaction.", "faqs": [{"question": "Do you take reservations?", "answer": "Yes, online or by phone. Walk-ins welcome based on availability.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Do you offer catering?", "answer": "Yes, drop-off and full-service catering for 10-500 guests.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Are you family-friendly?", "answer": "Yes, kids menu and high chairs available.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Do you accommodate dietary restrictions?", "answer": "Yes, gluten-free, vegan, and allergy-aware options.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Do you have private dining?", "answer": "Yes, private rooms for parties of 12-60.", "category": "general"}]}, {"name": "Restaurants - Frequently Asked Questions", "content": "Here are common questions and answers about our services:\n\nQ: Do you take reservations?\nA: Yes, online or by phone. Walk-ins welcome based on availability.\n\nQ: Do you offer catering?\nA: Yes, drop-off and full-service catering for 10-500 guests.\n\nQ: Are you family-friendly?\nA: Yes, kids menu and high chairs available.\n\nQ: Do you accommodate dietary restrictions?\nA: Yes, gluten-free, vegan, and allergy-aware options.\n\nQ: Do you have private dining?\nA: Yes, private rooms for parties of 12-60."}]'::jsonb, updated_at = now() WHERE industry_id = 'restaurants';
UPDATE public.industry_template_packs SET kb_seed_documents = '[{"name": "Construction - Services Overview", "content": "Welcome to our construction business. General contracting: home additions, kitchen and bath remodels, basement finishing, decks, custom builds, commercial buildouts, project management.\n\nServing residential and commercial customers with licensed, insured, and experienced professionals."}, {"name": "Construction - Pricing & Process", "content": "Our pricing approach for construction: Free estimates on projects over $5,000. Most kitchen remodels $25k-$80k; bath remodels $12k-$45k. Financing available.\n\nProcess: 1) Schedule a consultation or service visit. 2) Receive a detailed quote upfront. 3) Approve and we get to work. 4) Follow up to confirm satisfaction.", "faqs": [{"question": "Are you licensed and bonded?", "answer": "Yes, fully licensed general contractor, bonded, and insured.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Do you pull permits?", "answer": "Yes, we handle all permitting and inspections.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "How long does a kitchen remodel take?", "answer": "Typically 4-8 weeks depending on scope.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Do you provide design services?", "answer": "Yes, in-house design or we work with your designer.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Do you offer warranties?", "answer": "Yes, 1-year workmanship warranty plus manufacturer warranties.", "category": "general"}]}, {"name": "Construction - Frequently Asked Questions", "content": "Here are common questions and answers about our services:\n\nQ: Are you licensed and bonded?\nA: Yes, fully licensed general contractor, bonded, and insured.\n\nQ: Do you pull permits?\nA: Yes, we handle all permitting and inspections.\n\nQ: How long does a kitchen remodel take?\nA: Typically 4-8 weeks depending on scope.\n\nQ: Do you provide design services?\nA: Yes, in-house design or we work with your designer.\n\nQ: Do you offer warranties?\nA: Yes, 1-year workmanship warranty plus manufacturer warranties."}]'::jsonb, updated_at = now() WHERE industry_id = 'construction';
UPDATE public.industry_template_packs SET kb_seed_documents = '[{"name": "Fencing & Decking - Services Overview", "content": "Welcome to our fencing & decking business. Wood, vinyl, aluminum, chain-link, and composite fencing; deck construction and repair; gates and automatic gate operators; pergolas.\n\nServing residential and commercial customers with licensed, insured, and experienced professionals."}, {"name": "Fencing & Decking - Pricing & Process", "content": "Our pricing approach for fencing & decking: Free estimates. Wood fence $25-$45/linear ft. Composite decks $45-$75/sq ft installed. Repairs by quote.\n\nProcess: 1) Schedule a consultation or service visit. 2) Receive a detailed quote upfront. 3) Approve and we get to work. 4) Follow up to confirm satisfaction.", "faqs": [{"question": "Do you do free estimates?", "answer": "Yes, free on-site estimates with materials samples.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "How long do composite decks last?", "answer": "25+ years with minimal maintenance.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Do you handle HOA approval?", "answer": "We provide spec sheets and renderings to assist your HOA submission.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Can you replace just damaged sections?", "answer": "Yes, partial repairs and section replacements.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Do you install gates with openers?", "answer": "Yes, swing and slide gates with smart openers.", "category": "general"}]}, {"name": "Fencing & Decking - Frequently Asked Questions", "content": "Here are common questions and answers about our services:\n\nQ: Do you do free estimates?\nA: Yes, free on-site estimates with materials samples.\n\nQ: How long do composite decks last?\nA: 25+ years with minimal maintenance.\n\nQ: Do you handle HOA approval?\nA: We provide spec sheets and renderings to assist your HOA submission.\n\nQ: Can you replace just damaged sections?\nA: Yes, partial repairs and section replacements.\n\nQ: Do you install gates with openers?\nA: Yes, swing and slide gates with smart openers."}]'::jsonb, updated_at = now() WHERE industry_id = 'fencing';
UPDATE public.industry_template_packs SET kb_seed_documents = '[{"name": "Handyman & Cleaning - Services Overview", "content": "Welcome to our handyman & cleaning business. Honey-do lists, drywall, painting, mounting, furniture assembly, minor plumbing/electrical, deep cleaning, move-in/out cleaning, and recurring house cleaning.\n\nServing residential and commercial customers with licensed, insured, and experienced professionals."}, {"name": "Handyman & Cleaning - Pricing & Process", "content": "Our pricing approach for handyman & cleaning: Hourly $75-$125 (1-hr min). Cleaning $150-$350 by home size. Recurring cleaning discounts.\n\nProcess: 1) Schedule a consultation or service visit. 2) Receive a detailed quote upfront. 3) Approve and we get to work. 4) Follow up to confirm satisfaction.", "faqs": [{"question": "What can your handyman do?", "answer": "Most non-licensed home repairs and improvements - call to confirm.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Do you bring supplies?", "answer": "Cleaning supplies included; handyman supplies billed at cost.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Are your cleaners background-checked?", "answer": "Yes, all staff vetted and insured.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Do you offer recurring service?", "answer": "Yes, weekly, bi-weekly, and monthly plans with discounts.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "What''s your satisfaction guarantee?", "answer": "100% - we''ll return and re-clean if you''re not satisfied.", "category": "general"}]}, {"name": "Handyman & Cleaning - Frequently Asked Questions", "content": "Here are common questions and answers about our services:\n\nQ: What can your handyman do?\nA: Most non-licensed home repairs and improvements - call to confirm.\n\nQ: Do you bring supplies?\nA: Cleaning supplies included; handyman supplies billed at cost.\n\nQ: Are your cleaners background-checked?\nA: Yes, all staff vetted and insured.\n\nQ: Do you offer recurring service?\nA: Yes, weekly, bi-weekly, and monthly plans with discounts.\n\nQ: What''s your satisfaction guarantee?\nA: 100% - we''ll return and re-clean if you''re not satisfied."}]'::jsonb, updated_at = now() WHERE industry_id = 'handyman';
UPDATE public.industry_template_packs SET kb_seed_documents = '[{"name": "Security Systems - Services Overview", "content": "Welcome to our security systems business. Home and business security: alarm systems, cameras, smart locks, video doorbells, monitoring, access control, and commercial integration.\n\nServing residential and commercial customers with licensed, insured, and experienced professionals."}, {"name": "Security Systems - Pricing & Process", "content": "Our pricing approach for security systems: Equipment from $299. Monitoring $25-$50/month. Free security assessments. Commercial systems quoted.\n\nProcess: 1) Schedule a consultation or service visit. 2) Receive a detailed quote upfront. 3) Approve and we get to work. 4) Follow up to confirm satisfaction.", "faqs": [{"question": "Do you offer 24/7 monitoring?", "answer": "Yes, professional UL-listed monitoring.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Can I view cameras on my phone?", "answer": "Yes, all systems include mobile app access.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Do you install smart locks?", "answer": "Yes, including Schlage, Yale, and August integrations.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "What''s the contract length?", "answer": "Month-to-month or 36-month with discounted equipment.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Can you upgrade my old system?", "answer": "Yes, we take over most existing systems and add modern features.", "category": "general"}]}, {"name": "Security Systems - Frequently Asked Questions", "content": "Here are common questions and answers about our services:\n\nQ: Do you offer 24/7 monitoring?\nA: Yes, professional UL-listed monitoring.\n\nQ: Can I view cameras on my phone?\nA: Yes, all systems include mobile app access.\n\nQ: Do you install smart locks?\nA: Yes, including Schlage, Yale, and August integrations.\n\nQ: What''s the contract length?\nA: Month-to-month or 36-month with discounted equipment.\n\nQ: Can you upgrade my old system?\nA: Yes, we take over most existing systems and add modern features."}]'::jsonb, updated_at = now() WHERE industry_id = 'security_systems';
UPDATE public.industry_template_packs SET kb_seed_documents = '[{"name": "Solar - Services Overview", "content": "Welcome to our solar business. Residential and commercial solar installation, battery backup (Tesla Powerwall, Enphase), EV chargers, solar panel cleaning, and system monitoring/repair.\n\nServing residential and commercial customers with licensed, insured, and experienced professionals."}, {"name": "Solar - Pricing & Process", "content": "Our pricing approach for solar: Free solar consultation and design. Average residential system $18,000-$35,000 before incentives. 30% federal tax credit available.\n\nProcess: 1) Schedule a consultation or service visit. 2) Receive a detailed quote upfront. 3) Approve and we get to work. 4) Follow up to confirm satisfaction.", "faqs": [{"question": "How much can I save?", "answer": "Most homeowners save 50-90% on electric bills - free quote shows your specifics.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Do you offer financing?", "answer": "Yes, $0-down loans, leases, and PPAs available.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "How long does install take?", "answer": "1-3 days install; 4-8 weeks total including permits and PTO.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "What about battery backup?", "answer": "We install Tesla Powerwall and Enphase IQ Batteries for blackout protection.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "What warranties come with solar?", "answer": "25-year panel warranty, 10-25 year inverter, 10-year workmanship.", "category": "general"}]}, {"name": "Solar - Frequently Asked Questions", "content": "Here are common questions and answers about our services:\n\nQ: How much can I save?\nA: Most homeowners save 50-90% on electric bills - free quote shows your specifics.\n\nQ: Do you offer financing?\nA: Yes, $0-down loans, leases, and PPAs available.\n\nQ: How long does install take?\nA: 1-3 days install; 4-8 weeks total including permits and PTO.\n\nQ: What about battery backup?\nA: We install Tesla Powerwall and Enphase IQ Batteries for blackout protection.\n\nQ: What warranties come with solar?\nA: 25-year panel warranty, 10-25 year inverter, 10-year workmanship."}]'::jsonb, updated_at = now() WHERE industry_id = 'solar';
UPDATE public.industry_template_packs SET kb_seed_documents = '[{"name": "Personal Assistant - Services Overview", "content": "Welcome to our personal assistant business. Personal and executive assistance: scheduling, errands, travel coordination, household management, event planning, project support.\n\nServing residential and commercial customers with licensed, insured, and experienced professionals."}, {"name": "Personal Assistant - Pricing & Process", "content": "Our pricing approach for personal assistant: Hourly $45-$95 or monthly retainer packages. Custom scopes available.\n\nProcess: 1) Schedule a consultation or service visit. 2) Receive a detailed quote upfront. 3) Approve and we get to work. 4) Follow up to confirm satisfaction.", "faqs": [{"question": "Are you available remotely or in-person?", "answer": "Both - virtual, hybrid, or on-site arrangements.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Are you bonded and insured?", "answer": "Yes, fully bonded and insured for peace of mind.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "What''s your minimum commitment?", "answer": "5-hour minimum to start; ongoing retainers from 10 hours/week.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Do you handle confidential information?", "answer": "Yes, NDAs available; discretion is core to our service.", "category": "general"}, {"question": "Can you help plan an event?", "answer": "Yes, from intimate dinners to large gatherings.", "category": "general"}]}, {"name": "Personal Assistant - Frequently Asked Questions", "content": "Here are common questions and answers about our services:\n\nQ: Are you available remotely or in-person?\nA: Both - virtual, hybrid, or on-site arrangements.\n\nQ: Are you bonded and insured?\nA: Yes, fully bonded and insured for peace of mind.\n\nQ: What''s your minimum commitment?\nA: 5-hour minimum to start; ongoing retainers from 10 hours/week.\n\nQ: Do you handle confidential information?\nA: Yes, NDAs available; discretion is core to our service.\n\nQ: Can you help plan an event?\nA: Yes, from intimate dinners to large gatherings."}]'::jsonb, updated_at = now() WHERE industry_id = 'personal_assistant';

-- Re-seed for any existing companies whose pack was previously empty
DO $$
DECLARE r record;
BEGIN
  FOR r IN SELECT id FROM public.companies WHERE industry_vertical IS NOT NULL LOOP
    PERFORM public.seed_industry_pack_kb_for_company(r.id);
  END LOOP;
END $$;
